        public String publish()
        Publish the message to Mercury topic specified by TopicPublisher.topicName. MercuryMessage.timestamp is set automatically before publishing. If MercuryMessage.messageId was not previously set by withMessageId(String), then it would be automatically generated by TopicPublishersFactory.messageIdSupplier
        Returns:
        ID assigned to the published message by SNS.
